f:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Outranking is best suited for content creators, SEO beginners, budget teams, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. seoClarity, meanwhile, shines for enterprise SEO, data driven teams, large websites, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2020, Outranking describes itself as \"AI content strategy tool that automates SEO writing and optimization.\" seoClarity, established in 2009, positions itself as \"Enterprise SEO platform with unlimited data access and AI insights.\" With 11 years between them, seoClarity brings the maturity and proven track record of a veteran platform, while Outranking offers the fresh perspective and modern architecture of a newer entrant."}]]}]
10:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **seoClarity** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (7.0 vs 6.0), more features (10 vs 5). However, this does not mean Outranking is a poor choice — far from it. Outranking excels in its own right, particularly for content creators and SEO beginners.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value unlimited keyword tracking, go with seoClarity. If very affordable pricing matters more to you, Outranking is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
